Why is this module needed?

Flask is the bridge between Python/AI models and web applications. After building Machine Learning or Generative AI models, users need a way to interact with them through a browser. Flask provides that backend framework.

For example:

User
   ↓
Web Browser
   ↓
Flask Web Application
   ↓
Machine Learning / Gemini / LLM
   ↓
Prediction or AI Response

Without Flask:

Your Python code runs only in the terminal.
Other users cannot easily access your AI model.

With Flask:

Anyone can use your AI application through a web browser.
You can deploy it online and share a URL.

